---
title: Foolproof Apricot Chicken with Roasted Cauliflower & Celery Slaw
description: Mumbai-spiced chicken breast pair perfectly with the sweet and fruity flavour of apricots for a match made in food heaven. Add a crunchy celery slaw for freshness and lots of texture, and you’re on to a winner!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
